text: Diego Armando Barrón Neri (born 30 May 1997) is a Mexican footballer who plays as a midfielder for Venados of the Ascenso MX on loan from Pumas de la UNAM. ==References== ==External links== * at Official Liga MX Profile Category:1997 births Category:Living people Category:Mexican footballers Category:Association football midfielders Category:Venados F.C. players Category:Ascenso MX players Category:Liga Premier de México players Category:People from Tlalnepantla de Baz Category:Footballers from the State of Mexico
